Generate a private key:
openssl genrsa -out key.pem

Generate a Certificate Service Request (CSR)
openssl req -new -key key.pem -out csr.pem

Generate Certificate:
openssl x509 -req -days 9999 -in csr.pem -signkey key.pem -out cert.pem

Build and run the webapp. Access with https:// prefix on port 8080

DO NOT COMMIT OR PUSH TO GITHUB WITH THESE FILES IN THE PROJECT DIRECTORY - GIT DOES NOT LIKE IT. MOVE BACK IN AFTER PUSHING. MOVE TO ~ USING mv *.pem ~
